OL,3,CPSNI chief defiant over PM cash plea
OL,4,Cand sends message to Executive
OL,6,FPSNI Chief Constable Jon Boutcher has
OL,7,Fsaid he would be concerned if the PSNI
OL,8,Fis not 'front and centre' of the
OL,9,FExecutive's programme for government.
OL,11,FMr Boutcher was speaking at a meeting
OL,12,Fof the Northern Ireland Policing Board
OL,13,Fwhere he revealed a recovery plan to
OL,14,Fincrease the number of police officers
OL,15,Fover the next three years.
OL,17,FAfter facing criticism for asking the
OL,18,FPrime Minister for more money, the
OL,19,FChief Constable insists he did not
OL,20,Fbreak any protocol and was entitled to
OL,21,Fdo so.
